                            'MixTiles' V1.0

                          by Charles-N. Jacob

  'MixTiles' is a @{" Workbench game " link eplay} where the idea is to eliminate
all neighbouring tiles that are of the same colour. To complicate
matters a lttle, the tiles are placed in piles of 4 and only the
uppermost tiles in the piles can be associated with their
neighbours... and the more the number of neighbouring tiles of the
same colour there are, the better it is...

  Have fun!

